<div style="color: #777;background-color:white;text-align:center;padding:50px 80px;text-align: justify;">
  <h2 style="text-align:center;">About Us</h3>
  <p style="text-align:center;">This website is made for Chitkara Students Only</p>
  <p style="text-align:center;">We used to organize an unoffical trip in a time span of 3-4 months</p>
</div>
